--- !u!114 &1706050299
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1706050298}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7caf0bef1348e5a4b824a4287dde85fb, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DistorsionScene
  narrativeCanvas: {fileID: 1706050297}
  gameHUD: {fileID: 1160890905}
  dialogueUI: {fileID: 1258143683}
  rolandSeenAngelica: {fileID: 667672828}
  backScreen: {fileID: 642301518}
  distorsedRoland: {fileID: 1375720084}
  rolandRelise: {fileID: 1659351759}
  angelicaTalks: {fileID: 1510995817}
  distorsion: {fileID: 2041987543}
  timeParadox: {fileID: 1203117768}
  rolandEnd: {fileID: 640630194}
  voiceSource: {fileID: 1706050305}
  ambientAudioSource: {fileID: 1412041156}
  endingMusicSource: {fileID: 2058443069}
  dialogueText: {fileID: 1412041154}
  typingSpeed: 0.05
  fadeDuration: 2
  block1:
  - text: no..no..Angelica..
    voice: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 796fb3cc6bae0c143a02acc1b41be34d, type: 3}
  - text: Please dont leave me..Angelica,please,I need you...
    voice: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 4244d6bbd29c8e243bfb59aea9863397, type: 3}
  - text: Angelica no.. please...
    voice: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e37a9c06d9c481b4699d2d7309f9af0d, type: 3}
  - text: The years...by your side...were the...best of...my entire existence...thank
      you Roland...
    voice: {fileID: 8300000, guid: cde3433f31249b847a4b59a7e8f5c72e, type: 3}
  - text: '*And just like that, Angelica breathed her last, closing her eyes forever.*'
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  - text: '*After all...he was a pathetic being who couldn''t do anything...because
      of him, he lost everything...*'
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  - text: '*What would life be like now without Angelica? What would Roland do after
      all this...?*'
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  - text: '*All these questions might upset you...but that''s okay, I''m here to
      talk, let''s talk...*'
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  - text: '*LET ME INSIDE YOUR MIND...ROLAND*'
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  indexToChangeToAngelica: 3
  block2:
  - text: ' An..gelica..'
    voice: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9cf9ecd58b6004349932841da078ae1d, type: 3}
  - text: '*Finally, Roland  succumbed to distortion, bringing this story of pain
      and tragedy to a close*'
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  block3:
  - text: oh...
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  - text: this was un expected...
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  - text: is your will that strong?
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  - text: well..then..
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  - text: show me Roland, Break the rule of the City...
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  - text: '*Roland''s distortion caused Angelica''s E.G.O. equipment to join the
      distortion, which resulted in the fusion of two E.G.O. equipment of different
      classes, creating a conflict with the City''s rules.*'
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  - text: '*In other words, the approach of an event horizon that would disrupt the
      timescale was unavoidable.*'
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  block4:
  - text: ....
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  - text: Fascinating...Simply fascinating
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  - text: The original timeline was broken, so the city's will had no choice but
      to accept the new one created by your singularity.
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  - text: Now answer me, Roland...how are you feeling?
    voice: {fileID: 0}
  - text: '"I have nothing but my sorrow'
    voice: {fileID: 8300000, guid: ca02fb34f809a3e409e75d48747caa1b, type: 3}
  - text: ' and I want nothing more.'
    voice: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 20e4670fcbdcaa64483c8a364c62389d, type: 3}
  - text: It has been, it still is, faithful to me.
    voice: {fileID: 8300000, guid: adfd339b8a0c0ae4c820f4fe491e5848, type: 3}
  - text: Why should I begrudge it
    voice: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 948eb4f6e03e5794398707c1a7479741, type: 3}
  - text: ' since during the hours'
    voice: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e5b12604ab44b504ba9dec5c5ec7bac4, type: 3}
  - text: when my soul crushed the depths of my heart
    voice: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8928723dd9f9f7f4abf25d4757f8b6f1, type: 3}
  - text: it was seated there beside me?
    voice: {fileID: 8300000, guid: d7e629cbbec467547a50cf8bb126c5eb, type: 3}
  - text: 'Oh sorrow, I have ended, you see, by respecting you, because I am certain
      you will never leave me. Ah, I realize it: your beauty lies in the force of
      your being.Because I know that on the day of my final agony, you will be there,
      lying in my sheets, O sorrow, so that you might once again attempt to enter
      my heart."'
    voice: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 32c2df1ffd200c040954ee5b909af9db, type: 3}
  indexToRelise: 4
  playerInput: {fileID: 1957103919}
  playerAttack: {fileID: 1957103922}
